><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">由於三個軟體我都用過。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/gfauAF2SOYI_184.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/gfauAF2SOYI&t=184" target="_blank"><strong># Vocol AI 與其他逐字稿服務的比較</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">就簡單從逐字稿品質、功能多樣性。分析耗費時間。來說明我的使用心得。Good Tape逐字稿品質最好。但沒有AI分析。分析時間適中。雅婷的逐字稿品質尚可。有AI分析。但分析時間很長。Vocol AI的逐字稿跟雅婷差不多。但支援的功能最多。且分析時間是三者最短的。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後要稱讚一下Vocol AI的客服。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/gfauAF2SOYI_213.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/gfauAF2SOYI&t=213" target="_blank"><strong># 結論</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">之前Google Meet的線上錄音檔消失。跟客服說明後一天內就找回檔案。讓我對Vocol AI更有信心。如果這支影片對你有幫助的話。請幫我在影片下方點個喜歡。並且把這支影片分享給需要的朋友。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後別忘了訂閱泛科學院的頻道。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">我們下支影片再見囉。</p>

